</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;But what if you should survive a critical illness or critical accident? With today's medical breakthroughs, more and more Canadians are surviving critical illnesses (cancer, heart attack or stroke) and injuries from critical accidents.&quot;">
