  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"INSURANCE PRODUCT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A 20-year term life insurance policy offered by TD Insurance, with policy number 123 456 789, enclosed in the booklet."&lt;SEP&gt;"A 20-year term life insurance product offered by TD Life."&lt;SEP&gt;"A life insurance policy that provides coverage for 20 years with fixed premiums, helping secure the financial future of dependents in case of death."&lt;SEP&gt;"A life insurance policy that renews automatically every 20 years without a medical exam, providing coverage until age 80. Premiums are fixed per term and guaranteed not to increase until renewal."&lt;SEP&gt;"A life insurance policy with a 20-year term offered by TD."&lt;SEP&gt;"A life insurance policy with a 20-year term, offered by TD Life."&lt;SEP&gt;"A life insurance product offered by TD Insurance with a 20-year term, providing death benefit coverage for the policyholder."&lt;SEP&gt;"A life insurance product with 20-year term coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"A type of life insurance that provides coverage for a 20-year term with fixed premiums, renewable up to age 80, and can be converted to permanent insurance without a medical exam."&lt;SEP&gt;"The specific life insurance product offered by TD Insurance, with a 20-year term duration."&lt;SEP&gt;"The specific plan of insurance being offered."</data>
